commit.message: Added routes for performing operations on contacts
Added routes for performing operations on groups
Added route to update the user details
Added Location class which represents a location with a latitude and longitude, added withinRange() function to check if 2 locations are within a given range
Modified deserializeUser to return all the user attributes
Setup passport to authenticate with email and password
Added helpers for postgres, added sql to generate tables, added type definitions for models
Added middlewares for handling errors and verifying that the user is authenticated
